rows.label: qst701905_msg0001
rows.name:
Sorry for the wait. We
got the Dragon Incense.

rows.label: qst701905_msg0002
rows.name: Really...? Thank you.

rows.label: qst701905_msg0003
rows.name: Let me! I'll make it!

rows.label: qst701905_msg0004
rows.name: Do you know the recipe?

rows.label: qst701905_msg0005
rows.name:
I studied it after Marena-san told
me about the Dragon Incense.

rows.label: qst701905_msg0006
rows.name:
I got the other ingredients with
Teeco and Joey, so I'm all set.

rows.label: qst701905_msg0007
rows.name: Then please, go ahead.

rows.label: qst701905_msg0008
rows.name: Leave it to me!

rows.label: qst701905_msg0009
rows.name: Alright, it's done!

rows.label: qst701905_msg0010
rows.name: Freja, please drink it.

rows.label: qst701905_msg0011
rows.name: It's not going to be gross again...?

rows.label: qst701905_msg0012
rows.name:
I made it sweeter than
before, so it's fine!

rows.label: qst701905_msg0013
rows.name:
Trust me and Laura-sama and
the others, and drink it!

rows.label: qst701905_msg0014
rows.name: Okay...

rows.label: qst701905_msg0015
rows.name: *gulp*...

rows.label: qst701905_msg0016
rows.name: Huh...?

rows.label: qst701905_msg0101
rows.name: My body feels so light...

rows.label: qst701905_msg0102
rows.name: Amazing! This medicine is amazing!

rows.label: qst701905_msg0103
rows.name: I feel super good!

rows.label: qst701905_msg0104
rows.name: Super good! Yay!

rows.label: qst701905_msg0105
rows.name: It's super effective!

rows.label: qst701905_msg0106
rows.name: We did it!

rows.label: qst701905_msg0107
rows.name: Oh... Freja...

rows.label: qst701905_msg0108
rows.name: Mother!

rows.label: qst701905_msg0109
rows.name: I'm so glad...

rows.label: qst701905_msg0110
rows.name: Freja, how are you feeling?

rows.label: qst701905_msg0111
rows.name: I feel so much better!

rows.label: qst701905_msg0112
rows.name:
I can stand up just fine, and I
have the energy to walk again...

rows.label: qst701905_msg0113
rows.name:
At this rate, it looks like we can
take shelter at Fred-san's inn.

rows.label: qst701905_msg0114
rows.name: Yes!

rows.label: qst701905_msg0201
rows.name: I'm overflowing with so much energy...

rows.label: qst701905_msg0202
rows.name:
I think this is the
best I've ever felt.

rows.label: qst701905_msg0203
rows.name: I feel like I can stand, walk, and run!

rows.label: qst701905_msg0204
rows.name: Haha, just don't get too carried away.

rows.label: qst701905_msg0205
rows.name: Okay!

rows.label: qst701905_msg0206
rows.name:
At this rate, we might even
be able to get a ride on
Wotta-san's Divine Beast ship.

rows.label: qst701905_msg0301
rows.name:
Seeing my daughter so full of
life... It's like a dream...

rows.label: qst701905_msg0302
rows.name:
This is all thanks to you, Laura-sama,
Adel-sama... and everyone else.

rows.label: qst701905_msg0303
rows.name:
I don't know how I can
ever thank you...

rows.label: qst701905_msg0304
rows.name:
...That Dragon Incense was
obtained because many people
we've met lent us their strength...

rows.label: qst701905_msg0305
rows.name: All we did was deliver it.

rows.label: qst701905_msg0306
rows.name:
So please... don't worry
about thanking us.

rows.label: qst701905_msg0307
rows.name: Yes, that's right.

rows.label: qst701905_msg0308
rows.name:
Seeing Freja healthy and
happy is enough for us.

rows.label: qst701905_msg0309
rows.name: ...Thank you.

rows.label: qst701905_msg0310
rows.name: Well, that's one problem solved.

rows.label: qst701905_msg0311
rows.name:
Shin... After you write
about today in your diary,
please let me read it.

rows.label: qst701905_msg0312
rows.name: Why?

rows.label: qst701905_msg0313
rows.name:
I want to look back on
this wonderful day again.

rows.label: qst701905_msg0314
rows.name: Ask Kagutsuchi.

rows.label: qst701905_msg0315
rows.name:
I'm afraid I must refuse as
well. Let's have Minochi-san
write a book about it.

rows.label: qst701905_msg0316
rows.name:
No... Well, I was planning
to write about it anyway...

rows.label: qst701905_msg0317
rows.name:
Make sure you write
about how cool I was.

rows.label: qst701905_msg0318
rows.name: I don't recall Hikari doing anything...

rows.label: qst701905_msg0319
rows.name: True.

rows.label: qst701905_msg0320
rows.name:
What?! Maybe not for the
Dragon Incense, but I was
plenty useful before that!

rows.label: qst701905_msg0321
rows.name: Heh heh, what a lively bunch.

rows.label: qst701905_msg0322
rows.name: Um... Adel-sama.

rows.label: qst701905_msg0323
rows.name:
You said not to worry about a
reward, but there is one thing
I would like to give you...

rows.label: qst701905_msg0324
rows.name: What is it?

rows.label: qst701905_msg0325
rows.name:
I was feeding these to Freja since they're
supposed to be nourishing, but now that we
have the Dragon Incense, she'll be fine...

rows.label: qst701905_msg0326
rows.name:
Ah... I bought about a hundred jars
for my daughter, so I have a lot.

rows.label: qst701905_msg0327
rows.name:
So I was hoping you might
take some for your wife.

rows.label: qst701905_msg0328
rows.name:
Thank you for your concern.
My wife will be delighted.

rows.label: qst701905_msg0329
rows.name: Your wife? You're married?

rows.label: qst701905_msg0330
rows.name: Ah, did I not mention it?

rows.label: qst701905_msg0331
rows.name: She's at our home in Aletta.

rows.label: qst701905_msg0332
rows.name:
She's with child. I think
she'll be giving birth soon...

rows.label: qst701905_msg0333
rows.name: [ML:Feeling kind=Anger ]WHAAAAT?!

rows.label: qst701905_msg0334
rows.name: [ML:Feeling kind=Anger ]Really?!

rows.label: qst701905_msg0335
rows.name: [ML:Feeling kind=Think ]I had no idea...

rows.label: qst701905_msg0336
rows.name: I didn't tell you? My apologies.

rows.label: qst701905_msg0337
rows.name:
So you see, I must defeat Metsu
for Iira, and for my family.

rows.label: qst701905_msg0338
rows.name:
No, no! This is no time to be
running around helping people!

rows.label: qst701905_msg0339
rows.name: You have to go back to Aletta!

rows.label: qst701905_msg0340
rows.name: It's alright.

rows.label: qst701905_msg0341
rows.name:
If anything happens, Veritas
and Montos are there, as are
the rest of the resistance.

rows.label: qst701905_msg0342
rows.name: They'll handle it.

rows.label: qst701905_msg0343
rows.name: That may be, but...

rows.label: qst701905_msg0344
rows.name:
But first, to prevent such a
situation, let us all work
together to defeat Metsu.

rows.label: qst701905_msg0345
rows.name:
You're right. That is
something only we can do.

rows.label: qst701905_msg0346
rows.name: I know, but...

rows.label: qst701905_msg0347
rows.name: ...Yes.

rows.label: qst701905_msg0348
rows.name: For the people we've connected with...

rows.label: qst701905_msg0349
rows.name:
And for everyone in Iira,
and for the unknown people
of Alst as well...

rows.label: qst701905_msg0350
rows.name: We have to defeat Metsu.

rows.label: qst701905_msg0351
rows.name: Yes, that's the Laura I know.

rows.label: qst701905_msg0352
rows.name:
It's alright... With these
comrades, we can win.

rows.label: qst701905_msg0353
rows.name: Yes... Everyone, let's give it our all!

rows.label: qst701905_msg0354
rows.name: Yeah!
